      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a fantastic ride! This vehicle is in good condition and has been lovingly maintained, ensuring it's ready for many more miles of dependable service. It offers a smooth, comfortable drive and is the perfect choice for anyone looking for a reliable and high-quality pre-owned car!",
